@DOrsulak-SOLIEL you can modify the configuration of the trackball controls if you'd like. Please look at the docs here:
https://threejs.org/docs/#examples/en/controls/TrackballControls

For example, if you'd like to change the panning speed:
```js
myGraph.controls().panSpeed = 0.1;
```

